      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't look like there's blood or anything. i looked in the mirror and it just looks normal. i'm kinda dreading going to the doctors though, it feels like a lot of hassle for something that might just be a clogged ear. do you think it's worth actually going in right now or should i just wait a few days to see if it clears up on its own?",
