      "content": "i mean i get that, but i'm just super busy this week. if it was actually serious like a puncture or something, wouldn't it hurt a lot? it's not really painful, just really muffled and weird sounding. i feel like if i just use some ear drops or wait it out, the pressure will just equalize. you're pretty sure it's not an emergency if there's no pain?",
